<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.3.9">
<l>ēṭot tēntum nīḷi laivē leṅka ḷiravaṇaṉār</l>
<l>ōṭip pōṉār nāṅka ḷeyttō muyvatōr kāraṇattāl</l>
<l>cūṭip pōntō muṅkaḷ kōma ṉāṇai toṭarēṉmiṉ</l>
<l>kūṭik kūṭi yāṭu kiṉṟōm kuḻama ṇitūramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Rāvaṇa, who bears a spear with a long blade like a palmyra leaf,</l>
<l>Fled and left; we faltered. With [our] aim being surviving,</l>
<l>We adapted, crowning [ourselves] with your king’s crest.</l>
<l>Please, don’t attack! We are dancing all together to the kuḻamaṇitūram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
